c: 2
v: 124
t: "And (remember) when, Ibrahim (Abraham) was tried by his Lord with certain Commands; these he fulfilled. He (his Lord) said: \"I will make you an Imam (guide or example) to the Nations.\" He Ibrahim (Abraham) pleaded: \"And also (Imams) from my off-spring!\" He (his Lord) answered: \"But My Promise is not within the reach of evildoers"